#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "4812"
msgid "Kido"
msgstr "Kido"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "4816"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "4820"
msgid "Saejima"
msgstr "Saejima"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "4824"
msgid "Talk_Ojigi"
msgstr "Talk_Ojigi"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "4828"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "132_Kido"
msgid "You sure you wanna go, Saejima-san?"
msgstr "¿Vas a ir, Saejima-san?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "144_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah. Time to settle the score for all the shit\\r\nmy boss and I've been through since '85."
msgstr "Sí. Voy a ajustar cuentas por las que mi jefe\\r\ny yo tuvimos que pasar hace 25 años."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "156_Kido"
msgid "25 years is a long-ass wait, man."
msgstr "25 años es bastante tiempo, hombre."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "168_Saejima"
msgid "You're tellin' me, kid."
msgstr "Dímelo a mí, chico."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "180_Kido"
msgid "Only one problem. The streets are still swarming with cops."
msgstr "Solo hay un problema. Las calles siguen repletas de policías."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "192_Kido"
msgid "No way you'll make it to the Millennium Tower aboveground."
msgstr "Será imposible que salgas de aquí y vayas directo a la Torre Millenium."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "204_Saejima"
msgid "Then how do I get there?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿cómo puedo llegar allí?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "216_Kido"
msgid "Take the north side exit to go topside. Then,\\r\ngo underground from the back of the Millennium\\r\nTower and exit at the Shichifuku Parking Lot."
msgstr "Ve por la salida norte para ir a la superficie,\\r\nluego entra por la parte de atrás de la Torre Millennium\\r\nLuego sal por el estacionamiento Shichifuku."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "228_Kido"
msgid "Next, head to the rooftop from Pink Alley and go\\r\na little south before returning to ground level.\\r\nAfter that, head south from the ramen shop..."
msgstr "Luego sube a los tejados y baja cuando estés por los callejones de la calle Pink y avanza un poco al sur antes de bajar. Después ve al sur de la tienda de ramen."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "240_Kido"
msgid "Go through the basement parking lot, past the central sewer,\\r\nand come out a manhole in front of the Millennium Tower."
msgstr "Atraviesa el estacionamiento subterráneo, pasa la alcantarilla\\r\ncentral y sales por una tapa de alcantarilla frente a la Torre Millennium."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "252_Saejima"
msgid "Sounds pretty fuckin' complicated, but I think I got it."
msgstr "Suena bastante complicado, pero creo que lo entiendo."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "264_Kido"
msgid "You'll be fine as long as you can avoid the cops."
msgstr "Si logras evitar a los policías, deberías estar bien."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "276_Kido"
msgid "Sorry, man. Wish I could do more to help."
msgstr "... Lo siento. Al final, esto es lo único que puedo hacer por ti."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "288_Saejima"
msgid "Heh, ya done more than enough. Thanks for everything, Kido."
msgstr "Je, ya has hecho más que suficiente. Gracias por todo, Kido."

#. y4:line_status=translated
#. y4:translated_by=Keiner
msgctxt "300_Kido"
msgid "You bet."
msgstr "Saejima-san..."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "324_Kido"
msgid "You wanna catch some Z's before it gets dark, Saejima-san?"
msgstr "Saejima-san, ¿quieres descansar hasta la noche?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "336_Saejima"
msgid "Nah, not yet."
msgstr "No, aún no."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "348_Kido"
msgid "Oh, all right."
msgstr "Oh, está bien."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "360_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, I think I'll kick back a little."
msgstr "Sí, creo que voy a descansar un poco."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "372_Kido"
msgid "Sounds good."
msgstr "Me parece bien."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "384_Kido"
msgid "I'll go check out the best route for you to get\\r\nto the Millennium Tower in the meantime."
msgstr "Mientras descansas, buscaré la mejor ruta\\r\nhasta la Torre Millennium."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "420_Kido"
msgid "Not yet."
msgstr "Todavía no."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "432_Kido"
msgid "Alright."
msgstr "Está bien."

